data.description: Beautiful all brick center hall Colonial. Open floor plan with a great eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, first floor family room and a finished rec room. The rooms are spacious. This is a 5 bedroom home. Four bedrooms on the second floor. Master has a master bath. Fifth bedroom is on the third floor with a full bath. Lot size is just under a quarter acre. Walk to Coventry and Cain Park. Great location for University Hospital, Cleveland Clinic and Case Western Reserve University.
